                                 <date>16. 7. 1905</date> statt.</note></rs>, <date>1905</date></supplied></seg></seg></opener><p>Einen solchen <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01530-2"/>Gang<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01530-2">Gemeint dürfte der Arkadengang des <rs type="place" ref="#pmb48395">Stiftes Kremsmünster</rs> sein.</note> wünschen
               Ihnen <signed>Hugo</signed><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><signed><handShift scribe="#pmb2292"/>– Gerty.</signed></p></div>
